            <h3>Who are the MDR Team?</h3>
            <p>The team responsible for the MDR, as well as many of the other data-related projects in ECRIN, are:</p>
        
            <table>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <img height="200" width="200" src="/images/people/Christian.jpg" alt="Christian Ohmann photo" />
