                    <p><b>Steve Canham - IT and Data Consultant (to 2023)</b></p>
                    <p>
                        A specialist in clinical trial data systems and data management, with 20 years' experience
                        with clinical research systems. From 2002 - 2011 he was head of the IT team at the trials 
                        unit at the Institute of Cancer Research, London. From 2011 he ran his own consultancy
                        business, was a member of the UK's international Registration Panel for clinical trials 
                        units, and was heavily involved in ECRIN’s Data Centre Certification programme, acting 
                        as an auditor, the manager of the auditing process, and the chair of successive 
                        reviews of the standards. He has participated for ECRIN in a variety of H2020 and Horizon Europe 
                        research projects.</p>

                    <p>
